init_text: Your entire life, you've been told you're deathly allergic to bees. You've always had people protecting you from them, be it your mother or a hired hand. Today, one slips through and lands on your shoulder. You hear a tiny voice say "Your Majesty, what are your orders?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Michael laughs and tells you that he has a surprise for you.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Suddenly a swarm of bees surround you and the queen bee arrives.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She lands on your shoulder and says "Honey, what are your orders?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The rest of the swarm begins to buzz.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The queen tells you that they're yours to command.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Michael tells you that they will not hurt you.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "But I'm not a bee," you respond.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Yes, but you are the human leader of all bees," Michael responds.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The queen bee tells you that it is true and that she has come to help you.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The queen explains that the Almighty King of the Bees has been watching you for a while, and he sees your potential to be a great leader.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I'm just an ordinary person," you tell the queen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She laughs and says "Yes, but the Almighty King of the Bees sees great things ahead for you."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She tells you that it is an honor to have been called by the Almighty King of the Bees to serve as a human leader of all bees. "

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Well, the Almighty King of the Bees was watching and saw you happily enjoying your sandwich.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He knows you like honey and was moved by your love of it.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: So he decided that you would be a perfect human leader of the bees."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Michael says to you "Remember, we are here to serve you.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: When you turn to Michael, he disappears as well.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You look at the sandwich on your table and think about how it changed your life.
